criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  confirmed treated or untreated insulinoma patients;

          -  [68Ga]Ga-HBED-CC-exendin-4 and [68Ga]Ga-NOTA-exendin-4 PET/CT within two consecutive
             days;

          -  signed written consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  pregnancy;

          -  breastfeeding;

          -  known allergy against exendin-4;

          -  any medical condition that in the opinion of the investigator may significantly
             interfere with study compliance
